item.title: Help wit my server
item.dc:creator: @zezi111 zezi111
item.description:
@zezi111 wrote:

Ok, i’ll help. First open up hamachi and click on the triangle on bottom right corner. Then click join network. Make a username and pass and click ok. Make sure it’s online. Next go to control panel then security center then windows firewall and shut off your firewall. Go to the exceptions tab and click “Add port…” put hamachi for the name and put the port of your server for port. Then click ok.
